<exercise checkit-seed="0001" checkit-slug="P5" checkit-title="Expected Value">
    <statement>
                <p> Tao is gambling \$5 on rolling a 15 on a 17-sided die. If Tao wins, they win \$16, otherwise they forfit their bet. What is the expected value of this gamble?
                </p>
        
    </statement>
    <answer>
        <p>
            The expected value is <me>\frac{1}{17}(16) + \frac{16}{17}(-5) = -$3.76</me>
        </p>
    </answer>
</exercise>
